parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the instrument cluster can lead to inaccurate speedometer readings, faulty fuel gauges, and malfunctioning temperature gauges, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
Electrical system failures can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Ignition switch failure can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Clutch system failure can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
and clutch pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Exterior lighting failure can cause accidents or reduce visibility, especially at night.
The failure of the multi-function switch can cause the headlights, turn signals, and hazard lights to malfunction, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Headlights flash or shut off intermittently
clicking or buzzing noise from the turn signal stalk

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: high beams shut off while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear tail lights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: Water accumulation in the rear tail light assembly
rear tail lights shut off or malfunction
near crash due to tail light failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Corrosion of Brake Lines and Fuel Lines
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion of brake lines and fuel lines can cause brake failure, leading to accidents or loss of control, and potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
corrosion visible on brake lines and fuel lines.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Anti-Lock Braking System (ABS) and Traction Control
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning ABS and traction control systems can cause loss of control, accidents, or failure to stop, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: ABS and traction control lights illuminate
vehicle continues to move despite braking
brake pedal feels soft or spongy.
